Rating: 3
I had some trouble taking the cake out of the pan, which had been well oiled and floured. However, it still looked and tasted very good. I took out half a cup of sugar, but the cake was still a bit too sweet, so next time I will take out a full cup of sugar, use tart apples, add walnuts, as suggested, and maybe increase on the spices. The subtle orange flavor is great, and complements quite well the apples.

